{"tid":2506444,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋game]有無巴絲十幾年前玩過呢隻PSP game","createTime":"2021-04-27T10:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T10:16:53.000Z","uid":352409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f548522df774ce2111634f90eca10abf8e95ca04","tid":2506444,"uid":352409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:16:53.000Z","msg":"八到九歲個陣我玩過隻psp game遊戲機制好有趣，但因為係日文搵唔番個遊戲..<br />\n求下你地睇下有無辦法搵番我童年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻game是咁的:<br />\nrpg升lv打怪,日文字(應該係日本game黎?)<br />\n遇怪後會入左個場景,主角可以跑黎跑去,一路風箏隻怪一路用魔法<br />\n入面有隻拎住掃把既粉紅色女法師可以召喚水龍捲同火球術打啲怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個遊戲機制好特別，唔係回合制，<br />\n好少game係2006-2008年出有類似依家啲傳說對決咁既機制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n好想搵番個隻game，睇番個隻game既中文攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}